Package dslabs.framework

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Address
    Addresses are opaque objects that uniquely identify Nodes.
    Application
    Applications are simple data structures used by your Nodes.
    Client
    Clients are a special case of Node.
    Command
    An operation on an Application.
    Message
    Base interface for all messages in the system.
    Result
    The value returned by an operation on an Application.
    Timer
    Base interface for all timers in the system.
